          "notes": "Strong narrative architecture grounded in documented case studies (Netflix, Amazon, Target, Duolingo) with rigorous concept accuracy and appropriate vocabulary calibration. However, D5 (Applied Outcome) is the critical weakness: lab activities are conversational with no executability constraints, and learners cannot verify capability delta without structured outputs or measurable deliverables.",
